#### Island Browser

#### Overview

This dashboard provides visibility into device activity and compliance within the Island Browser platform.

Filters allow you to refine by device type, OS platform, and status. Key metrics highlight active, archived, and jailbroken devices for a quick health snapshot. Visualizations include policy updates over time, device distribution by status, type, OS platform, and browser update status.

A table of top MDM providers and essential device details such as IDs, IPs, MAC addresses, users, and organizations which supports monitoring and auditing.
